# Adminer — no required env vars.
# Connect to any DB container by entering its hostname, credentials, and DB name in the UI.
# DB hostnames reachable from Adminer:
#   personal-net: nextcloud-db, immich-db, mealie-db, linkwarden-db,
#                 vikunja-db, paperless-db
#   infra-net:    gitea-db, woodpecker-db
